00:26:27.470 --> 00:26:31.370
less than what everybody ought
to want to do with their life.

00:26:31.370 --> 00:26:33.420
So I've been very lucky
to work with this group,

00:26:33.420 --> 00:26:34.948
and I enjoy it a great deal.

00:26:38.020 --> 00:26:41.160
I thought I'd start by,
maybe bragging a little bit

