And this was the Violence
Against Women Act

00:27:16.010 --> 00:27:19.670
Reauthorization, and this
was a huge crowd of people.

00:27:19.670 --> 00:27:22.371
And I will-- and, as you see
in this photo, a lot of folks

00:27:22.371 --> 00:27:23.870
here, the Violence
Against Women Act

00:27:23.870 --> 00:27:27.360
was a coalition much broader
than Indian country itself.

00:27:27.360 --> 00:27:29.870
The National Task Force
to End Domestic Violence,

00:27:29.870 --> 00:27:33.430
and all kinds of folks
are involved in that.

00:27:33.430 --> 00:27:35.237
So I want to-- in
addition to that,

00:27:35.237 --> 00:27:37.570
some of the other recent
things that this administration

00:27:37.570 --> 00:27:40.120
and tribal leaders have achieved
working together, amendments

