massively improved processes,
much quicker land into trust

00:28:04.950 --> 00:28:07.250
processes, land into
trust in Alaska, which

00:28:07.250 --> 00:28:08.960
is going to be a
great step forward,

00:28:08.960 --> 00:28:12.200
and then a lot of
reservation proclamations.

00:28:12.200 --> 00:28:15.170
There'd been quite a number of
settlements in Indian country,

00:28:15.170 --> 00:28:18.100
the Cobell settlement for
mismanagement of Indian trust

00:28:18.100 --> 00:28:23.299
funds, 86 tribal cases
over $2.8 billion.

00:28:23.299 --> 00:28:25.590
The Contract Support Litigation
for self-determination,

00:28:25.590 --> 00:28:28.730
and self-governance
contracts, about $1.5 billion

00:28:28.730 --> 00:28:32.210
there, about $2 billion worth
of water rights settlements,

00:28:32.210 --> 00:28:34.640
the Keepseagle settlement
for discrimination

00:28:34.640 --> 00:28:37.520
against Native American
farmers, altogether, this

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:40.320
might be about $10 billion in
settlements for Indian country

00:28:40.320 --> 00:28:42.260
that tribes have
worked with Congress,

00:28:42.260 --> 00:28:44.970
and the administration, to
achieve over the last seven

00:28:44.970 --> 00:28:46.710
years.

